        {
            "jpName": "素直なウマ娘",
            "enName": "Honest Horsegirl",
            "jpText": "スカーレットさんとスペさんが、ワーストワンツー……！？",
            "enText": "Scarlet and Spe came in dead last?!",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 133,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 145,
                    "pathId": 3839983334189853760
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 145,
                    "pathId": -9189423695065766329
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 175,
                    "pathId": -5326387271167536048
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": -8199300085951801763
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3585360677774685411,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "情報ツウなウマ娘",
            "enName": "Well-informed Umamusume",
            "jpText": "スカーレットさんは熱があったらしいけど、スペさんは\r\nなんでだろう。ていうか、なんかぽっちゃりしたような……？",
            "enText": "I know Scarlet recently had a fever, but I wonder why Spe \ndid so poorly? Actually… she looks like she might've gained \nsome weight, but…",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 294,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 305,
                    "pathId": -1804047277217846196
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": 8806713613476599599
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 130,
                    "pathId": 6872521257354944253
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 77,
                    "pathId": -710659688568473213
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6697425514587983797,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "2人",
            "enName": "Both",
            "jpText": "……うっそぉ……！",
            "enText": "Nooooo!",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 57,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 42,
                    "pathId": 5045154404810877263
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 38,
                    "pathId": -7891881592093684105
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 42,
                    "pathId": 8933378538868981252
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 38,
                    "pathId": 1959352988624500351
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6594062050439648631,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "はぁ、はぁ、はぁ……！\r\nもう、あんな走りしちゃダメだ！　もっと、もっとがんばらなきゃ！",
            "enText": "<i>Huff… Huff… Huff!</i> I can't afford to run like that anymore! \nI have to work even harder!",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 225,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": 4627805187491294517
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": -7509006451162595279
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8894408560862192900,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "――って！　もう1か月経つのに全然調子戻らないよ！\r\nどうしたらいいべか、お母ちゃん！",
            "enText": "Gah! It's been a month already, but I still can't get out \nof my slump! What should I do, Mom?!",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 222,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 244,
                    "pathId": -1405638101326823486
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 5292422439665310929
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1861624023282471162,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペの母親",
            "enName": "Spe's Mother",
            "jpText": "『したっけ、1回ちゃんとゆっくりしなって！\r\nアンタ、聞いた感じだと休みなくトレーニングしてんだろ？』",
            "enText": "Listen, you need to step back and take it easy! \nFrom what you've been tellin' me, you've been \ntraining nonstop, right?",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 256,
            "voiceIdx": 7,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 268,
                    "pathId": 2704696580840477077
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7550678136654984083,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "ちゃ、ちゃんと休んでるよ！\r\nしっかり寝てるし、ゆっくりお風呂にも浸かってるし――",
            "enText": "I-I <i>have</i> been resting properly! I sleep well, take relaxing baths…",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 193,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 268,
                    "pathId": -5888577067650258869
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": -1458184126225808483
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3209982734740553426,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペの母親",
            "enName": "Spe's Mother",
            "jpText": "『そういうんじゃなくて！　誰かと遊んだり、どっか出かけたり\r\nリフレッシュするってことさ。やってないっしょ？』",
            "enText": "That's not what I mean! I mean going out and having fun \nwith your friends to refresh yourself. You haven't been \ndoing that, have you?",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 259,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 270,
                    "pathId": -2473512048646653491
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 270,
                    "pathId": -7499006211052309361
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5515850684479553672,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペの母親",
            "enName": "Spe's Mother",
            "jpText": "『騙されたと思ってさ、1回遊んでみな？　パーッと全部忘れる\r\nってのが、案外解決の糸口になったりするもんなのよ』",
            "enText": "Just trust me! Give it a try. Let go of aaall your worries for \na while and you might just find that it solves your problem.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 291,
            "voiceIdx": 10,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 303,
                    "pathId": -6491359978927563591
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 302,
                    "pathId": -3797180526018302509
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1869914481584152951,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "それは、そうかもしれないけど……。",
            "enText": "I… I suppose that's true…",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 121,
                    "pathId": -8698304518740768488
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -1523619597892625766
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8492594335103824088,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "で、でもさ、全然走れるようになってないのに\r\n遊ぶなんて、そんなの、サボってるみたいで……！",
            "enText": "B-But if I go and hang out with friends now before getting \nmy running back on track, I'd just be slacking off…!",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 259,
            "voiceIdx": 12,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 248,
                    "pathId": 2944801678390159800
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": -4317129300538109482
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8058301711143502389,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "ママから、贈り物？\r\nなにかしら。",
            "enText": "Mama sent me something? I wonder what it is.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 106,
            "voiceIdx": 13,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": -7755853767249899644
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": 5053657047946950093
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 33,
                    "pathId": -670609586504345251
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": 7409047867951563148
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1225769664947680746,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『水着を贈ります。最近、忙しそうね。\r\nたまには、海やプールへ遊びに行ってね。ママより』",
            "enText": "\"I hope you like the swimsuit I got you. You've been so \nbusy lately. Take some time to visit the beach or pool \nonce in a while, dear. Love, Mama.\"",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 102,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 131,
                    "pathId": -6515925531987613767
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5086533474418738782,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "へえ！　かわいい水着。遊びに行ってね、か。\r\n嬉しいけど……でも、急にどうしたんだろ。",
            "enText": "Wow! What a cute swimsuit! \"Visit the beach or pool,\" huh? \nI'm glad she's thinking of me, but I wonder why the sudden gift.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 310,
            "voiceIdx": 14,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 318,
                    "pathId": -8556342375788508743
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 170,
                    "pathId": -7774351985656627993
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3119343750096607719,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "ママ、仕事で忙しいし、\r\nいつもアタシのことはアタシに任せてるのに――あ。",
            "enText": "She's so busy with work and usually leaves me \nto my own business, so why… Oh…",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 240,
            "voiceIdx": 15,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 251,
                    "pathId": -5692097191389197230
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 33,
                    "pathId": -8465570336827172571
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6347056035948281558,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "（……もしかして、模擬レースで結果がダメダメだったこと、\r\n知ってるの？）",
            "enText": "(Could it be she knows how horribly I did \nin the recent practice race?!)",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 139,
            "voiceIdx": 16,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 176,
                    "pathId": -1053871047262204340
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 895504796335253082
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1148567498708031894,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "（それで、自己管理が甘いって思われたとか……？\r\nううん、考えすぎよ。そんなことある、わけ……）",
            "enText": "(Maybe she thinks I'm doing a poor job of taking care of myself \nbecause of that…? No, I'm overthinking things. There's no way \nshe could've…)",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 280,
            "voiceIdx": 17,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 291,
                    "pathId": -5800048616212969431
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -6945782068622755838
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2402504552533322580,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "…………。",
            "enText": "……",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "voiceIdx": 18,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 4,
                    "pathId": 983229732560407351
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6653732505924415841,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "う～～っ、\r\n次こそ絶対、レースで1番になったって報告してみせなきゃ！",
            "enText": "<i>Ngh!</i> I'll definitely win the next race and make sure \nshe knows I got first place!",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 183,
            "voiceIdx": 19,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 45,
                    "pathId": -5675892710238543071
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 70,
                    "pathId": -3072396303208197760
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -126171211964377340,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "はぁ……。昨日は結局、ケンカになっちゃった……。",
            "enText": "<i>Sigh…</i> I can't believe I ended up arguing with Mom yesterday…",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 176,
            "voiceIdx": 20,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 29,
                    "pathId": -3276297945256071806
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": -8984497438877784184
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": 4951206932397927290
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": 4343928020945948445
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3275496217373596937,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "って、せっかくグラウンドに来てるのに時間もったいない！\r\n切り替え、切り替え！　今日はけっぱるぞー！",
            "enText": "Ugh, what am I doing, wasting my time out here \non the racetrack? I've gotta focus! I'm going to \nnail training today!",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 240,
            "voiceIdx": 21,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 34,
                    "pathId": 7052944827380390269
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -613374737621271965
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8849785147285545121,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "やっぱりいた！\r\nあの、よかったら併走しませんか？",
            "enText": "I had a feeling she'd be here! \nUm, would you like to run with me?",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 148,
            "voiceIdx": 22,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 27,
                    "pathId": -2994532774096318053
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 2004159195004922058
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 5703817095548633975
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1768858888590901328,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "『――この間の模擬レースから調子が戻らないんです。なにしても\r\n上手くいかなくって。その、スペさんもそうですよね……？』",
            "enText": "\"I haven't been able to get back into shape since \nthe practice race the other day, no matter what I do. \nHas it been the same for you, Spe?\"",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 280,
            "voiceIdx": 23,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 295,
                    "pathId": -4294020549121207867
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 308,
                    "pathId": -4888707610780182444
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 2369710986095811049
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8721763286863276010,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "『そ、そうです！　考えれば考えるほどフォームとかわかんなく\r\nなっちゃって。前は普通にできてたことのはずなんですけど……』",
            "enText": "\"Y-Yeah! The more I think about it, the more confused I get \nabout my running form. But everything was fine before…\"",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 303,
            "voiceIdx": 24,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 172,
                    "pathId": 164820666331829198
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 290859512658270106
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 314,
                    "pathId": 381901824568771113
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4126462516509278981,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "『わかります。アタシもそんな感じです……。それで、レース\r\nみたいに誰かと競り合えば調子が戻るんじゃないかなって――』",
            "enText": "\"I know what you mean. I'm in the same boat. That's why \nI thought challenging someone to a race might help me \nget back into stride, so…\"",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 279,
            "voiceIdx": 25,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 290,
                    "pathId": -6145694819699417573
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": 1864676853085878582
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 5364947170411399482
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5090734640099473199,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "スペシャルウィーク",
            "enName": "Special Week",
            "jpText": "（……土煙、足音、スカーレットさんの背中。\r\nうん、そうそう、レースってこんな匂い！　思い出してきた！）",
